{"tid":494773,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[數學普及] Measure Theory (測度論)簡介","createTime":"2017-12-10T04:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T08:25:42.000Z","uid":66324,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"520be700a414f7cc5e53d52d6a30084b339ebadd","tid":494773,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:45:54.000Z","msg":"如果有乜講錯的話, 歡迎指出<br />\n<br />\n香港某大學Math major的Required course入面有一科令眾多學生叫苦連天, 考試題目median幾乎係0. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個post會假設學生有M1/M2的Calculus, 再加set notation, cardinality<br />\n好啦, 有基本微積分咪算lor, 做乜搞咁多野姐? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-------<br />\n<br />\nQ1. Suppose f: [0, 1] -&gt; R defined by<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4cpd6n5v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4cpd6n5v&h=2c5fde7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFind the area under the graph of f.<br />\n<br />\n好啦, 你一定諗都唔諗就寫左 <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2yfz0djt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2yfz0djt&h=908c9b36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出黎啦<br />\n當小學雞, 咁不如將countable咁多條線痴埋, 咁線係無area, 咁痴埋都無area (as taking limit) 咯係咪?<br />\n首先: 究竟呢舊野有無意義先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問返Riemann integral係乜: 將[0, 1]斬開任意n等份, 然後再係上面揀一點(叫x_n) 再計f(x_n)係乜, 當個n越黎越大, 如果佢會趨向一個數字, 而且呢個數字係同揀咩x_n無關, 個integration符號先有意思<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/d5ishbeo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd5ishbeo&h=87dcbc07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Source: Wikipedia)<br />\n<br />\n由於rational同irrational numbers都係dense ge, 所以係任何interval上面都有一點rational一點irrational, 咁就出事啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (點解出事呢?)<br />\n<br />\n-------<br />\n<br />\nQ2. 學過probability都知expectation (or expected value) 就係個random variable (payoff function) 的平均值, 可能大學first course教你integrate 個random variable, 之但係...<br />\n<br />\nQ1' 而家玩抽獎, 由[0, 1]抽一個number, 抽中rational你有一蚊, 抽中irrational你無錢收, 問expected value係乜? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-------<br />\n<br />\nQ3. 讀左first course in analysis 就given一個sequence of integrable functions f_n, 如果f_n converge to f uniformly, 即係<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i8vekqpx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi8vekqpx&h=a17fd2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就可以自由交換 limit同 integral, 即係<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4qjb2vg7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4qjb2vg7&h=8a3449d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之但係uniform convergence 呢個條件好harsh, 如果知 pointwise convergence (即係 lim f_n (x) = f(x) for all x), 有無D容易D check到的條件令上述的野成立先?<br />\n(係分析學入面, 交換limit sign同other sign係幾common的問題)<br />\n<br />\n-------<br />\n<br />\nQ4. 而家given一個subset of real numbers, 例如<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bpf39lga\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbpf39lga&h=c46910bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求長度, (答案: pi^2/6)<br />\n但係呢, 呢度有infinite個disjoint intervals, finite就知點加姐, infinite呢?<br />\n<br />\n-------<br />\n<br />\n如果熟知elementary analysis的朋友, 就知Riemann integral係用step functions去estimate, 而step function的area係堆長方形<br />\n即係: <img src=\"https://holland.pk/70yfnue2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F70yfnue2&h=5c56613e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nx_i strictly increasing, 我地知道 <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8rsen0hf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8rsen0hf&h=ad2a0883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家砌integral的基本砌圖不如唔好只限intervals, 一D夠靚的set就可以啦, 咁乜野叫夠靚ge set呢, 呢D就叫<span style=\"color: red;\">measurable sets</span> (即係有length/area/volume, 可以係0, 總之係一個數字或者infinity).<br />\n<br />\n好啦, 咁而家我地有個世界, 叫做 X (覺得好無安全感的可以將 X 當哂做 R), 同埋有一堆我地可以計到&quot;volume&quot;的subsets, 叫 A, 我地想:<br />\n<br />\n1. 無野當然0 volume, empty set要係 A 入面<br />\n2. 成個世界我地都想知體積啦, 所以 X 都要係 A 入面<br />\n3. 當 E 係 A 係面, X\\E 都要係 A 入面 (一個紙箱, 放左D野係入面, 剩返的體積就咁減)<br />\n4. 如果我地有一堆countable有體積的 sets union 哂佢當然想計到體積啦 (countable的其中一個technical的原因係我地要take limit)<br />\n<br />\n符合以上條件的話, 我地會叫 A 做 <span style=\"color: red;\">sigma-algebra</span><br />\n<br />\n然後要有一個function計佢地的volume, 究竟呢個function要有咩properties, 好簡單, 如果有countable咁多個mutually disjoint measurable sets (即係任何兩舊野都無相交), 好似痴泥膠咁, 希望就咁加就算, 所以連同empty set要volume zero, 個function要有以下三個條件:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/k63yigw8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fk63yigw8&h=33ef4d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6n19s0dx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6n19s0dx&h=431cbf48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xwapo2en\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxwapo2en&h=fdbdc971&s={SIZE}\" />, E_i mutually disjoint<br />\n<br />\n呢種的function我地叫<span style=\"color: red;\">measure</span>. (註: \\mu(E)可以係positive infinity)<br />\n<br />\n總結黎講, 個世界(X, A, \\mu) 定義左乜野subset係measurable, 同埋定義左個measure, 呢種空間我地叫<span style=\"color: red;\">measure space</span><br />\n(無\\mu的情況, 我地叫 (X, A) 做<span style=\"color: red;\">measurable space</span>)<br />\n<br />\n例子:<br />\n1. (廢話系列 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 乜撚volume都0咪算 (想像real line係平面上高, 咁自然乜subset都係area zero)<br />\n2. (Counting measure) 就係計個subset有幾多粒elements, 如果無限就無限<br />\n3. Length, area, volume 都係, 但係呢個複雜少少, 之後會再講下<br />\n4. Probability (measures), 望清楚probability個定義<br />\n<br />\n下次講 measure 有乜性質"},{"pid":"34fded2dd9b279dd868c1753ec52ab65b0364e1f","tid":494773,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:54:20.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"249fa841d22e053340cee824b4df053748406538","tid":494773,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ee/Riemann.gif/220px-Riemann.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fe%2Fee%2FRiemann.gif%2F220px-Riemann.gif&h=d2f77f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nwiki幅圖load唔到, 係度補番"},{"pid":"0011247b30281e5a52d7e8421d89a992049b4930","tid":494773,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814725141ccf3fd709780d412ed3f58237f7a926","tid":494773,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:05:45.000Z","msg":"Anal 專家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527f8d2a02726e91a8a52f47e553df292bdfb356","tid":494773,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Anal 專家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你先鍾意玩anal <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2e3d92cf1cca64fe316bfab9d70f360491746f","tid":494773,"uid":54173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"Ho ball"},{"pid":"a7414e1645f09d939f38c0e3e85700d3c11d13cb","tid":494773,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"Too difficult didn't read<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dda6e67766badd03155b7a32f6857c22dcb7a0b","tid":494773,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ee95fbfec38fd7a62bb38f756c9fa893eb2e50fa","tid":494773,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Too difficult didn't read<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊度唔明, 講下, 等我望下之後可以點再貼地d"},{"pid":"d10f8a7d9f893bc7dfb701f9094e42028a94f35b","tid":494773,"uid":111804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"median 0咁咪好多人要retake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40b451c1d31783cd0c9b44ce540ebcc45c6a298","tid":494773,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:24:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>median 0咁咪好多人要retake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有30-40%送分膠計題 (唔好問我點解real analysis會用膠計題), 同埋midterm絕大部份人都近乎full mark<br />\n只係final剩低果60-70%就... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4eb756795296d9e5d2f6e1c9c513b47db2e6024","tid":494773,"uid":54173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Too difficult didn't read<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊度唔明, 講下, 等我望下之後可以點再貼地d</blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得成篇野如果本身無學過都好難睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b45ecc2cd7e9f78bf3d3d867b9611745c6faeb","tid":494773,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Too difficult didn't read<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊度唔明, 講下, 等我望下之後可以點再貼地d</blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得成篇野如果本身無學過都好難睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n篇野好似無乜數學content <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大約只係講左d motivation 同個definition點黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你覺得可以點講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a1861a7f086495cb17fe903706584b92946a37","tid":494773,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:28:08.000Z","msg":"留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢科好難"},{"pid":"a75d65819defdf67120a1e519794cb0fab476012","tid":494773,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢科好難</blockquote><br />\nConcept唔難，但exericse難到痴線"},{"pid":"707d0db02f1bb5b76fdcb5a071ac39807c89cbd7","tid":494773,"uid":80183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"想問measure theory係屬於real analysis?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係基本analysis 野咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a9740147772065e310596a3a3a6fe02f3cf725","tid":494773,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Too difficult didn't read<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n簡單黎講，中學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用開既叫 Riemann Integral<br />\n<br />\nRiemann Integral 係用好細好細既長方形去估計面積<br />\n<br />\n長方形 = 長 x 寬<br />\n<br />\n有 d 數學人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痕<br />\n創建左 Riemann Integration 處理唔到計 function<br />\n<br />\n解決方法係 ：<br />\n重新建立 measure 一個 set 既方法"},{"pid":"e5049998c2a9510f94c609ff0338c326fbaa3817","tid":494773,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問measure theory係屬於real analysis?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係基本analysis 野咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nElementary analysis同measure theory 都係Real analysis<br />\n不過一般undergrad唔會教abstract measure theory, 但應該會有lebesgue measure on R<br />\n但我覺得由abstract measure theory開始先會比較好，之後再睇番lebesgue measure on R"},{"pid":"c59c6daa3da24caf9b4bc0a00da33ac25a4f5b70","tid":494773,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問measure theory係屬於real analysis?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係基本analysis 野咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nElementary analysis同measure theory 都係Real analysis<br />\n不過一般undergrad唔會教abstract measure theory, 但應該會有lebesgue measure on R<br />\n但我覺得由abstract measure theory開始先會比較好，之後再睇番lebesgue measure on R</blockquote><br />\nanalysis既數學真係唔係人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4789a9f6f909bff36d8d209ae49b08b7bafe9a67","tid":494773,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Too difficult didn't read<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n簡單黎講，中學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用開既叫 Riemann Integral<br />\n<br />\nRiemann Integral 係用好細好細既長方形去估計面積<br />\n<br />\n長方形 = 長 x 寬<br />\n<br />\n有 d 數學人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痕<br />\n創建左 Riemann Integration 處理唔到計 function<br />\n<br />\n解決方法係 ：<br />\n重新建立 measure 一個 set 既方法</blockquote><br />\n唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痕啦<br />\n就算係riemann integral 有時都會借lebesgue integral過橋"},{"pid":"88c45dac0e65b01d7a69103839a2bfc9d316ca30","tid":494773,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問measure theory係屬於real analysis?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係基本analysis 野咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nElementary analysis同measure theory 都係Real analysis<br />\n不過一般undergrad唔會教abstract measure theory, 但應該會有lebesgue measure on R<br />\n但我覺得由abstract measure theory開始先會比較好，之後再睇番lebesgue measure on R</blockquote><br />\nanalysis既數學真係唔係人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但measure theory 讀pprobability都要識架喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20629b1cbe150b1cfafdf6c4d5e8314194909e79","tid":494773,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢科好難</blockquote><br />\nConcept唔難，但exericse難到痴線</blockquote><br />\n等你講解下 CLT，Law of large number, convergence<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae472327782a809934717471f09eb0ed155aba7","tid":494773,"uid":118823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:53:36.000Z","msg":"數學系兜踎留個名先"},{"pid":"92c56b7ba71c0fc0376dfa5b78208d3107669714","tid":494773,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢科好難</blockquote><br />\nConcept唔難，但exericse難到痴線</blockquote><br />\n等你講解下 CLT，Law of large number, convergence<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係probability ge 範圍啦喎<br />\n一般measure theory 唔太關心呢d 野，但都可以講下ge"},{"pid":"87e9ea5d1a93e66961d05fd109640d65b69a2110","tid":494773,"uid":37416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"巴打講得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkg